The Discrepancy between Needle Biopsy and Radical Prostatectomy Gleason Score in 
Patients with Prostate Cancer.

Abedi AR(1), Basiri A(2), Shakhssalim N(3), Sadri G(4), Ahadi M(5), Hojjati 
SA(6), Sheykhzadeh S(7), Askarpour S(8), Ghiasy S(9).

Author information:
(1)Department Of Urology, Shohadae-tajrish Hospital, Shahid Beheshti University 
Of Medical Sciences,tehran, Iran. arabedi_80@yahoo.com.
(2)Department Of Urology, Shahid Labbafinejad Medical Center, Urology and 
Nephrology Research Center, Shahid Beheshti. basiri@unrc.ir.
(3)Department Of Urology, Shahid Labbafinejad Medical Center, Urology and 
Nephrology Research Center, Shahid Beheshti. slim456@yahoo.com.
(4)Department Of Radiology. Iran University of Medical Sciences, Tehran, Iran. 
ghazaal.sadri@yahoo.com.
(5)Department Of Pathology , Shohadae-tajrish Hospital, Shahid Beheshti 
University Of Medical Sciences,tehran, Iran. mahsaamehr@yahoo.com.
(6)Department Of Urology, Shohadae-tajrish Hospital, Shahid Beheshti University 
Of Medical Sciences,tehran, Iran. sah_hojjati@yahoo.com.
(7)Department Of Urology, Shahid Modares Hospital, Shahid Beheshti University Of 
